&lt;p&gt;Looking for a new challenge?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Sirona care &amp; health are looking for a well organised; enthusiastic; experienced administrative assistant to join our Safeguarding Children’s Team in Bristol.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for someone who has excellent communication skills and can execute high quality pieces of work under pressure. The work is fast paced and you will be exposed to highly confidential information which can be emotionally impactful.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The successful candidate will be supported by an established team of safeguarding specialist nurses and administrator and will be part of the wider integrated safeguarding team in Sirona care and health The post holder will need to have an awareness and understanding of confidentiality, GDPR and Information Governance.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a full time, 6 months fixed term post and will be based at either Southmead house or Osprey court, Bristol.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you have any questions about the post, please contact:&lt;br /&gt;Fiona Gilbert (Named Nurse for Safeguarding Children Bristol) 07880 053000&lt;br /&gt;Or email helen.owen9@nhs.net&lt;/p&gt;
